(19, 1, 'tes', 'Ifnu bima', '2012-07-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[ilkomerz] [LOWONGAN] QA Lead di Blibli.com', NULL, NULL, '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC ''-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN'' ''http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd''>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<body style=''background-color: #fff;''>\r\n<span style=''display:none''>&nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<!--~-|**|PrettyHtmlStartT|**|-~-->\r\n<div id=''ygrp-mlmsg'' style=''position:relative;''>\r\n  <div id=''ygrp-msg'' style=''z-index: 1;''>\r\n<!--~-|**|PrettyHtmlEndT|**|-~-->\r\n\r\n    <div id=''ygrp-text'' >\r\n      \r\n      \r\n      <p>Dear Moderator, mohon ijin posting lowongan kerja ya.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe, blibli.com, have opening for QA lead position. Blibi.com is<br>\r\necommerce site under PT Global Digital Niaga, a company under Global<br>\r\nDigital Venture that own by Djarum group. This is a very exciting and<br>\r\nchallenging job in startup company but backed by huge and settled<br>\r\ngroup. So you get both startup working environment and a good package<br>\r\njob.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSend your resume to me <a href=''mailto:ifnubima%40gmail.com''>ifnubima@gmail.com</a>, and If you have anything to<br>\r\nask about this job, please feel free to contact me at twiiter<br>\r\n@ifnubima or gtalk ifnubima.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nResponsibilities:<br>\r\n- Responsible for automation test suite development, execution and debugging<br>\r\n- Writing automated test cases using automation tool for new features<br>\r\nadded and enhancing exiting test suite<br>\r\n- Developing automation test cases and creating test data based on<br>\r\nmanual test cases or new features implemented<br>\r\n- Running regression tests as part of on-going agile development<br>\r\n- Writing test plans and test cases from product and design specifications<br>\r\n- Black box testing following existing test plans<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQualifications and Skills Required:<br>\r\n- 5+ yrs of QA/Testing experience in a quality assurance role with<br>\r\nfocus on automation QA<br>\r\n- Experience in testing software products in JAVA/J2EE and Web environment<br>\r\n- Good working knowledge of Windows, Linux and database technologies<br>\r\n- Good knowledge of shell, Perl, Python or other scripting languages<br>\r\n- Experience implementing API-level test cases is highly desirable<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks,<br>\r\n<br>\r\n-- <br>\r\n<a href=''http://ifnubima.org/indo-java-podcast/''>http://ifnubima.org/indo-java-podcast/</a><br>\r\n<a href=''http://tanyajava.com/download/javadesktop''>http://tanyajava.com/download/javadesktop</a><br>\r\n<a href=''http://tanyajava.com/download/scrum''>http://tanyajava.com/download/scrum</a><br>\r\n@ifnubima<br>\r\n<br>\r\nregards<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n     \r\n\r\n    <!--~-|**|PrettyHtmlStart|**|-~-->\r\n    <div style=''color: #fff; height: 0;''>__._,_.___</div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n  \r\n   \r\n    <div id=''ygrp-actbar'' style=''clear: both; margin-bottom: 10px; white-space: nowrap; color: #666; padding-top: 15px;''>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <a href=''mailto:ifnubima@gmail.com?subject=Re%3A%20%5BLOWONGAN%5D%20QA%20Lead%20di%20Blibli%2Ecom'' style=''margin-right: 0; padding-right: 0;''>\r\n	  Reply to <span style=''font-weight: 700;''>sender</span></a> |\r\n        <a href=''mailto:ilkomerz@yahoogroups.com?subject=Re%3A%20%5BLOWONGAN%5D%20QA%20Lead%20di%20Blibli%2Ecom''>\r\n	  Reply to <span style=''font-weight: 700;''>group</span></a> |\r\n        	  <a href=''http://groups.yahoo.com/group/ilkomerz/post;_ylc=X3oDMTJyZTkxdm45BF9TAzk3MzU5NzE0BGdycElkAzIwMDk1NjMxBGdycHNwSWQDMTcwNTI0MDU2MARtc2dJZAMxMDg5MgRzZWMDZnRyBHNsawNycGx5BHN0aW1lAzEzNDM3MjEwODI-?act=reply&messageNum=10892''>Reply <span style=''font-weight: 700;''>via web post</span></a> |\r\n            	<a href=''http://groups.yahoo.com/group/ilkomerz/post;_ylc=X3oDMTJmdHRobDZ2BF9TAzk3MzU5NzE0BGdycElkAzIwMDk1NjMxBGdycHNwSWQDMTcwNTI0MDU2MARzZWMDZnRyBHNsawNudHBjBHN0aW1lAzEzNDM3MjEwODI-'' style=''font-weight: 70